<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .bg-greyish {
            background-color: #c9c9c9;
        }
      
        .card-body {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .card-subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .card-text {
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        .text-muted {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        .d-flex.justify-content-center {
            justify-content: center;
        }
        #about-section h2,
        #contact-section h2 {
            text-align: center;
        }
      
        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: white !important;
        }
        .content {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .footer {
            position: relative;
            left: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #ac3b61;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog</title>
</head>
<body>
    
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            
            <div class="col" id="about-section">
                 <h2>About</h2>
                <p>Welcome to InterviewInSight! We are a platform dedicated to sharing interview experiences and insights to help job seekers navigate their career paths.</p>
                <p>Our goal is to provide a valuable resource where individuals can learn from real-life interview stories, gain knowledge about various companies, job roles, and preparation strategies.</p>
                <p>Whether you are a recent graduate, a career switcher, or simply looking for interview tips and inspiration, you'll find a wealth of information and experiences shared by our community of contributors.</p>
                <p>Join our platform, share your own interview experiences, and contribute to the growth of our knowledge base. Together, let's empower each other to succeed in our professional journeys!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col" id="contact-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>Have a question, feedback, or suggestion? We'd love to hear from you!</p>
                    
                    <div class="contact-info">
                        <div class="contact-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                            <p>Email: akshatguptakth@gmail.com</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                            <p>Phone: +91 6205794180</p>
                        </div>
                        
                    </div>
                    
                    <p>Feel free to reach out to us with any inquiries. We'll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.4/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
